KARDIA LEXICON

**Category Universe — Complete Candidate List**

**Purpose: **The authoritative backlog of all categories the Kardia Lexicon will build toward. Organized into 10 semantic groups across three phases. Every entry is subject to GR-01 through GR-11. This document is the master scope reference for the generator, the lexeme map, and the editorial review process.

