| נַחֲלָה | nachalah | P2 | pre-exilic | Inheritance — covenant portion and identity |
| עַם | am | P2 | pre-exilic | People — covenant community defined by YHWH |
| גּוֹי | goy | P2 | pre-exilic | Nation — people defined by land and governance |
| מִדְבָּר | midbar | P2 | pre-exilic | Wilderness — formative covenant space |
| מָיִם | mayim | P2 | pre-exilic | Waters — primordial chaos and purification |
| אוֹר | or | P2 | pre-exilic | Light — God's ordering presence, not photons |
| בָּרָא | bara | P2 | pre-exilic | Create — God's exclusive ordering act |
| יָצַר | yatsar | P2 | pre-exilic | Form/fashion — potter-work intimacy with creature |
| תּוֹהוּ וָבֹהוּ | tohu vavohu | P2 | pre-exilic | Formless/void — pre-order, not evil chaos |
| שָׁמַיִם | shamayim | P2 | pre-exilic | Heavens — God's throne and sphere of governance |
| בְּרֵאשִׁית | bereshit | P2 | pre-exilic | In the beginning — temporal ordering, not cosmogony |

