| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| εἰρήνη | eirene | P3 | nt | Shalom in Greek dress — whole-community flourishing |
| πίστις | pistis | P3 | nt | Covenant faithfulness — via emunah, not mere belief |
| ἀγάπη | agape | P3 | nt | Chosen covenant love — via ahavah/chesed |
| χάρις | charis | P3 | nt | Covenantal gift — via chen/chesed |
| δικαιοσύνη | dikaiosyne | P3 | nt | Right-relatedness — via tsedaqah |
| λόγος | logos | P3 | nt | Word as event — via dabar, NOT Stoic reason |
| εὐαγγέλιον | euangelion | P3 | nt | Royal covenant announcement — not just good news |
| βασιλεία | basileia | P3 | nt | Kingdom — God's covenant ordering reign |
| μετάνοια | metanoia | P3 | nt | Full re-orientation — via teshuvah/shub |
| ἀνάστασις | anastasis | P3 | nt | Resurrection — bodily, via techiyat hametim |
| ἐκκλησία | ekklesia | P3 | nt | Assembly — covenant community, via qahal |
| κύριος | kyrios | P3 | nt | Lord — rendering YHWH, covenantal sovereignty |
| χριστός | christos | P3 | nt | Anointed — covenant agent, via mashiach |
| δόξα | doxa | P3 | nt | Glory — via kavod, not mere praise or reputation |
| ἅγιος | hagios | P3 | nt | Holy/saint — via qodesh, set-apart community |
| σωτηρία | soteria | P3 | nt | Salvation — corporate deliverance, via yeshua |
| κοινωνία | koinonia | P3 | nt | Covenant participation/sharing — not fellowship program |
| παράκλητος | parakletos | P3 | nt | Advocate/comforter — covenant mediating presence |
| καιρός | kairos | P3 | nt | Appointed covenant moment — not clock time |
| αἰών | aion | P3 | nt | Age/world — via olam, covenant era not eternity |
| ζωή | zoe | P3 | nt | Life — covenant vitality, via chayyim |
| ἁμαρτία | hamartia | P3 | nt | Missing covenant mark — via chata |
